{
  "_comment": "Proxuma Design System 2.0 -> Vega-Lite config. Merge this object into the `config` key of every data-chart spec (PATH A) so figures bind to real data and render on-brand and deterministically. Tokens are authoritative; do not introduce red/green or off-spec blues. Bad/negative = muted slate #8A93A6, never red. Emphasis = cyan #00B7FF, primary = navy #164387.",
